snippet.title: Haxor - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Haxor is out today, 12.04.2019! Travel back in time to 8bit era in this retro-shooter with oldschool, pixel-art visuals! Travel through 4 different worlds, kill hundreds of monsters and fight with big bosses. Use powerful special skills and iconic rocketjumps to survive!

Learn more about Haxor:

Steam: http://bit.ly/HaxorGame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/fatdoggg
Twitter: https://twitter.com/FatDogGames
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fatdoggames
